page.content:
{Wild flowers,}some of the flowers we saw on our walk. Birdsfoot Trefoil, Bugle, Buttercup, Red Campion, Clover, Catsear, Charlock, Chick Weed, Hedge/ Cow Parsley, Cowslip, Creeping Cinq- foil, Ladies Smock, Daisy, Dandelion, Dead Nettle, Dock, Dog Rose, Forget- me-not, Goosegrass, Garlic, Ground Ivy, Hedge Mustard, Travellers Joy, Vetch, Herb Robert, Herb Bennet, Hop Trefoil, Hogweed, Mayweed, Meadow Sweet, Plantain, Poppy, Ragged Robin, Ragwort, Scarlet Pimpernel, Shepherds Purse, Silverweed, Sorrel, Speedwell.
This project was compiled by ...... The lower junior children from Hillesley C.E.V.A. School, with their teacher Mrs. J.P.A. Harper, also with help from other members of the school and local people.
